up against a wall and hang them!

87
00:05:00,938 --> 00:05:03,873
But, Major Burns,
there is the Christian ethic.

88
00:05:03,941 --> 00:05:09,208
I know that! I won a white Bible at my church...
for organ playing. So lay off!

89
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:13,148
[Potter] Never yell at a priest, Burns.
It's a sure ticket to hell. More suction.

90
00:05:13,217 --> 00:05:15,879
It's a waste of time,
saving these slant eyes.

91
00:05:15,953 --> 00:05:18,046
[Potter] They're also collateral.
I'm trying to arrange...

92
00:05:18,122 --> 00:05:20,488
a swap of their prisoners
for our prisoners.

93
00:05:20,558 --> 00:05:22,355
Okay, finished.
Can I help anybody?

94
00:05:22,426 --> 00:05:25,088
- I'm fine. Got this bowel by the tail.
- <i>B.J.?</i>

95
00:05:25,162 --> 00:05:27,096
