Ahh...

439
00:23:30,219 --> 00:23:32,949
Aha!
I got it!

440
00:23:33,022 --> 00:23:35,650
Last one right in her nose.
All 15!

441
00:23:35,724 --> 00:23:37,715
- Look! Look!
- Very nice, Frank.

442
00:23:37,793 --> 00:23:40,421
- [B.B.'s Rolling]
- Ohh!

443
00:23:40,496 --> 00:23:43,693
- What happened?
