444
00:23:43,766 --> 00:23:46,360
- I did?
- You did it on purpose.

445
00:23:46,435 --> 00:23:48,926
Every time I do something special,
you spoil it.

446
00:23:49,004 --> 00:23:51,029
So do it again.

447
00:23:51,106 --> 00:23:53,734
Do it again, he says. Hmph!

448
00:23:53,809 --> 00:23:56,959
Three days. Three days.

